### Business Logic & Inference Layer

#### [NEW] [src/utils/age.ts](file:///c:/Users/kingh/OneDrive/Documents/giziku/src/utils/age.ts)
* High-precision age calculation logic in years and months.
* Rules for selecting questionnaires:
  * 0 - 2 Years: Balita (Toddler)
  * 3 - 5 Years: Prasekolah (Preschool)
  * 6 - 12 Years: Anak Sekolah (School Age)
  * >12 Years: Remaja / Dewasa (Teen/Adult)

#### [NEW] [src/services/ai.ts](file:///c:/Users/kingh/OneDrive/Documents/giziku/src/services/ai.ts)
* Integrates `@onnxruntime/react-native` for loading ONNX models.
* Implements a **robust fallback engine** that runs heuristic and questionnaire-based local diagnosis when the ONNX native runtime is unavailable (e.g., when testing in Expo Go) or when no model file is found.
* Translates image outputs to find nutritional or psychological visual signs (like conjunctiva pallor, fatigue lines, nail health).

